snippet.title: Live Coding: PyQt5 GUIs w/ Python
snippet.description:
Let's build a couple basic GUI applications using PyQt5. We'll build a simple Bitcoin price checker. We'll also look at how to package the application as a .exe, .app, and .deb for distribution.
